<%@ page pageEncoding="UTF-8" %>
<section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-01.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.7787878787878788" data-w="660" type="block"  /></section><p data-start="173" data-end="332" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">今晚的节目，我们请来了一位很多渥太华朋友其实已经很熟悉的艺术家。就算您很少关注艺术和绘画，也一定曾在屏幕上刷过“轻轻地吹”的美篇作品——那些关于光影、季节和渥太华城市风景的画面，很多都出自她的镜头。她用相机记录渥太华的自然风光、人文景致，也记录着岁月在这座城市里缓缓流淌的痕迹。她，就是路风老师。</span></p><p data-start="173" data-end="332" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><p data-start="334" data-end="449" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">路风老师是一位仫佬族艺术家，毕业于广西艺术学院美术系装潢专业。她早年的专业创作，曾获得中南五省设计奖，也在美国《富达杯》亚太艺术大奖赛中获奖；在艺术创作中，她还曾为丁玲的散文集《我在爱情中生长》设计封面。</span></p><p data-start="334" data-end="449" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><p data-start="457" data-end="560" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">1992 年旅居欧洲之后，她选择在渥太华定居，并创办了路风美术教育中心。这一做，就是三十多年。三十多年来，她一直坚守在美术教育一线，连续二十二年获得《加拿大国际儿童艺术展》优秀指导老师奖，并获得终身成就奖。</span></p><p data-start="457" data-end="560" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><p data-start="562" data-end="607"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">今晚，就让我们一起，通过她的讲述，慢慢走近路风老师，听听她在艺术、教育和生活中的那些故事。</span></p><ul style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;" class="list-paddingleft-1"><li style="white-space:pre-wrap;list-style-type:none;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><section><div class="lf-audio-card"><i class="fa fa-volume-up"></i><div><b>&#38899;&#39057;&#65306;</b>&#36335;&#39118;-&#33402;&#28023;&#27969;&#20809;&#65288;&#19978;&#65289;<br/><span>&#21407;&#33410;&#30446;&#38899;&#39057;&#26102;&#38271;&#32422;35&#20998;&#38047;&#65292;&#21487;&#36890;&#36807;&#21407;&#24494;&#20449;&#25991;&#31456;&#25910;&#21548;&#12290;</span></div></div></section></li></ul><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="">嘉宾：路风</span></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="">91年出国之前，我在桂林民族师范（现桂林理工大学）任美术教研组负责人，讲师。倡导师范美术图案课的改革，撰文《民族师美术范图案课教学改革的探索》并且携带课堂里学生的设计作品，参加八八年广西全省师范美术中心教研组的年会评比。被评为优秀论文奖的一等奖。大学毕业后设计的“千里光中草药香皂包装设计”两次获市优秀设计奖，“小溪香皂包装设计”获广西省包装设计奖，“千里光组合香皂包装设计”获中南五省优秀设计奖。十年来的专业设计和高校教学工作，让我个人认为，我的学生都应该向更专业的高度迈进，即使他们未来只是一名中、小学教师，而不是美术设计师，也应该掌握一些设计技能和创意技巧。</span></b></p><section style="text-align: center;"><b style="font-weight: normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf=""><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="">到了欧洲，走在郁金香盛开、画廊占陆地面积是世界上最多的阿姆斯特丹，在卢森堡、比利时的大街小巷，在卢浮宫蒙娜丽莎的原作前，在巴黎圣母院的钟楼上，在摇滚乐、爵士乐舞台林立，通宵达旦庆祝音乐节的欢乐情景下，让我看到了耳目一新的西方艺术世界和丰富多彩的表现形式。中国艺术家应该如何在西方的土地上发声，展现自己的才华？我跃跃欲试。我和当时作研究的丈夫租住一位苏里南老华侨的套间，每晚途经房东的床前进入到我们的卧室。一铺床，一张茶几。我以茶几为桌子，凳子高矮不和，就跪在地毯上作画。在阿姆斯特丹举办画展，作品入驻当地的画廊。一腔热情展示中国艺术和中国文化。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-02.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.6686390532544378" data-w="338" height="181" style="width:445px;height:298px;" width="270"  /></span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span></section><section style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-03.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7151162790697675" data-w="344" height="197" style="width:447px;height:320px;" width="275"  /></span></span></span></section><section style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-04.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7034883720930233" data-w="344" height="194" style="width:450px;height:317px;" width="275"  /></span></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></section><section><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">主持人：</span><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">中国艺术家应该如何在西方的土地上发声，展现自己的才华？这是一个特别好的问题，也是困扰很多移民艺术家的问题。通过上面的分享，我们看出欧洲经历</span><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">让路风老师收获了很多，她看到了耳目一新的西方艺术世界和丰富多彩的表现形式</span><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">那么定居加拿大以后，是什么原因让她选择自己创办画室呢？</span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></p></b></span></section><section><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">路风：</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">丈夫拿到奖学金到加拿大读硕、博，到了蒙特利尔周边的人知道我的情况后，一致建议我办学。于是，我在报纸上刊登广告，接到第一单生意是上门教三位麦吉尔医学院博士后的小孩们画画，蒙特利尔大学博士生的孩子也找上门来了。这些家长后来都成为了我的朋友。但是我仍然希望获得一个当地的文凭并在当地找一份和美术有关的工作。于是小女儿出生后丈夫用童车推着她，陪同我去参加蒙特利尔美术院校的入学考试。当我把作品放在课桌上，坐下来环视坐满教室的考生时，监考老师走过我的旁边看了一眼，直接走进办公室。一会儿，三、四位老师出来围着我看作品窃窃私语。除了看作品，还现场素描静物写生。另外还有一个英语摸底考试，主要是为了分班。成绩出来时，负责的老师对我说，您的美术功底和创作能力已经超出了我们的教师水平，而同时您的英语基础也超出了我们的教学范围，实在没有更低的班了。她问我为什么要入学，我说为了找工作。她说你直接去找啊。我说英语不好，她说你就去学英语啊。没必要浪费时间再来学美术嘛。于是我痛下决心攻英语，一周上两个英语班，但还是想学一些西方的美术理念和现代设计的技术，尤其是电脑设计。半年后，顺利入读某私立设计学院，将刚满周岁的女儿送到邻街的日托。放学回来去接女儿，推开阿姨家的门，大冬天门窗密封的”托儿所”烟雾缭绕，刺鼻的烟味扑面而来。男主人是个烟民。一周不到，将女儿转到十几里以外的，几窗明净，设施齐全，拥有几位硕士教育学位毕业老师任教的幼儿园。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 离开母亲进入新环境的女儿常常发烧，一周内半夜带她去医院看过三次急诊。没有药吃。直到某天半夜女儿手握耳朵大哭，再带她去看儿科医生，才开始吃抗生素。转耳鼻喉科检查，诊断为耳朵发炎流脓，处理意见，如果不好一年后引流。</span></p><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;">放学后去幼儿园接孩子，在白雪皑皑的幼儿园游乐场，她站在雪地里，听不见妈妈叫她，听力丧失。我很难受，我是要上学，还是要女儿的健康? 最后，母爱的责任占据了上峰，毅然而然退学在家照顾孩子。等她恢复身体后再上学吧。半年后，孩子痊愈，我再度奔赴又一个设计学院的考场。准备入学时，丈夫找到工作，我们搬迁到渥太华，与蒙特利尔我的学生成为了邻居。在两家的走访中提起了我想升学的愿望。那对家长博士夫妇再次呼吁：“您没必要去读书，应该办学！”很快便介绍了他们同事的孩子来跟我学画，又为我找来了小区附近的学生。路风画室由此萌生，传授技能，举办学生画展。学生的各种写生作品发表在《中华导报》《健康时报》《七天新闻》《渥京周末》等报刊上。路风美术逐渐在渥太华家喻户晓。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: normal;"><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-05.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7224489795918367" data-w="490" height="283" style="width: 531px;height: 384px;" width="392"  /></span></p><o:p></o:p></b></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-06.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8838951310861424" data-w="534" height="378" style="width:517px;height:457px;" width="427"  />&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-07.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.7316176470588236" data-w="272" height="377" style="width:231px;height:400px;" width="218"  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-08.jpg" alt="20251129_231044a" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.3829787234042554" data-w="329" height="364" style="width:289px;height:400px;" width="263"  /></span></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-09.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.739344262295082" data-w="610" height="361" style="width:521px;height:385px;" width="488"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-10.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.9345955249569707" data-w="581" height="434" style="width:537px;height:502px;" width="465"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-11.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7786259541984732" data-w="524" height="326" width="419"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 15px;">《</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 15px;">2024</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 15px;">风景写生》作者：</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 15px;">Anton Yan</span></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-12.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7805343511450382" data-w="524" height="327" width="419"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 15px;">《帆船俱乐部写生》作者：</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 15px;">Aiden Chi</span></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-13.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7803030303030303" data-w="528" height="330" width="422"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11pt;line-height: 115%;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">《风景写生</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11pt;line-height: 115%;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">-</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11pt;line-height: 115%;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">帆船俱乐部》作者：</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11pt;line-height: 115%;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">Daniel Chen</span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf="">8</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11pt;line-height: 115%;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></section><section><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">主持人：</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">路风画室蒸蒸日上，在多元文化中重新理解“创意”的意义，带领学生们打造一个真正</span><span leaf="">属于孩子们的艺术世界。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">路风：</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">《2013年第十一届加拿大国际儿童艺术展暨中国-加拿大国际儿童艺术交流展》于2013年12月27号在北京举行，由陶行知教育基金和加拿大中加文化理事会联合举办，陶行知微梦基金会承办。艺术展的主题是：舞动绿色，畅想未来。中国、加拿大儿童送展作品100多幅，作者年龄在5岁到17岁各族裔的孩子们。中国同学的作品是书法，加拿大送去的50幅作品中，路风美术有29幅无一雷同，极具创意、同学们亲手绘制的绘画原创作品参加展览。加拿大中加理事会主席周先生发函说：“路风老师您好！你们的作品在中国非常受欢迎。”新华社、凤凰网、中国青年网、陶行知基金会、北京七一小学报道了展览消息。新华社报道的标题为《“中加儿童艺术展”助提艺教文化内涵》。</span></p><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">微梦基金秘书长李小唤女士在开幕式上对记者说道：“在中国，寄希望于艺术的人很多，但是真正因此改变的人却寥寥。因为，我们的艺术教育偏重素质传授，忽</span><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">视了保护儿童天马行空的艺术天性。艺术需要天赋和激情，公益需要爱心和热忱。一个书画交流展承载不下太多的内容，但却可以通过它提升中国孩子的艺术想象力和鉴赏水平，传递艺术带给孩子们的满足和快乐! 以中加两国小朋友的</span><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">画作作为起点，未来我们还要将引进其他国家的儿童画作，打造一个真正属于孩子们的艺术世界。”</span></p></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></section><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.75pt;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-14.jpg" alt="http://study.ifeng.com/uploads/news/20131227/13881340306235.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.6657963446475196" data-w="383" height="204" style="width:432px;height:288px;" width="306"  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.75pt;"><span leaf="">（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.75pt;"><span leaf="">2013</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.75pt;"><span leaf="">年）陶行知教育基金会微梦基金秘书长李小唤女士发言</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><section style="text-align: left;"><b style="font-weight: normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">手持原中国设计、教学10年的历史，于20多年前踏上西方的土地，经欧洲到北美，创办路风画室的那一刻，我便明确提出“创意在先，基本功后来”的办学方针。开创了“创意在先”路式美术教育的道路。2003年加拿大国际儿童艺术展向我抛出橄榄枝，从第二届加拿大国际儿童展起，我便率领青少年艺术家驰骋于艺术沙场，摘得无数的金果、银果、铜果…..近几年来，几乎将树上80%的果果摘回家来。</span></p><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">美国藤校，加拿大名校也特别喜欢我们的同学们。哈弗大学、康奈尔大学、全美最具开拓性的商学院宾夕法尼亚大学沃顿商学院、英国牛津大学、麦吉尔大学、多伦多大学、 麦克马斯特大学、滑铁卢大学、女皇大学、卡尔顿大学、渥太华大学……都有同学们的身影。遍布艺术、医学、法律、计算机、电子工程、商学……各种学科。</span></p><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">个人认为，创意教育不专属于培养艺术家而存在，它可以是培养有高感性能力、创造力、同理心、右脑活跃适应社会各界有开拓素质的人才的。时至今日，“创意在先，基本功教学后来”的美术教育行之有效。不敢说日后诺贝尔奖的皇冠会戴在同学们的头上，起码腾校、名校青睐有创造能力、有艺术气质、关爱社会公益的青少年是不争的事实。</span></p><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">2013年第十一届加拿大国际儿童艺术展暨中国—加拿大国际儿童艺术交流展于12月27日结束北京之行，按原计划应该于春节返回老家多伦多展览。后应主办方的邀请，展览在中国其它城市巡展，并在3月份北京东城少年宫展出后，评出奖项。 路风美术送的29幅作品，荣获1个金奖，1个银奖，4个铜奖，6个优秀奖，1个最佳创意奖，16个参赛奖。路风美术获组织奖，路风老师获伯乐奖。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">根据中加儿童艺术展的情况，我撰文《创意在先 领艺教风骚》和《舞动绿色 畅想未来》在渥太华《中华导报》2014年2月14日的社区新闻中发表。</span></p><span style=""><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></b><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-15.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.3196480938416422" data-w="341" height="360" style="width:400px;height:528px;" width="273"  /></span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-16.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8651399491094147" data-w="393" height="272" style="width:422px;height:365px;" width="314"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">Mary Wang 12</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;Food chain disappearance&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><section><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">2013</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">年第十一届加拿大国际儿童艺术节暨中国</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">-</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">加拿大国际儿童艺术交流展》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">金</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="">奖</span></span></section><section><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"></b></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">主持人：您如何带学生在国际艺术展中屡获佳绩？</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></span></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></span></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">路风：</span></span></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">2003</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">年，总部在多伦多的“加拿大国际儿童艺术展”主席先生通过电话，向在渥太华的我们抛出了橄榄枝，邀请我们参加加拿大国际儿童艺术展。同学们勤于绘画基本功的训练从来没有参加过任何比赛，一下子就参加国际比赛，同学们能行吗？怀着试试看的心情，我们欣然接受了邀请。我组织同学们创作，把作品寄往多伦多参加《</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">2003</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">年第二届加拿大国际儿童艺术展》。</span></span></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></span></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-17.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7707129094412332" data-w="519" height="320" style="width:429px;height:331px;" width="415"  /></span></span></section><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;" data-pm-slice="4 3 []"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes;"></span><span leaf="">Mona Li&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">（李玥）</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">7</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁《加拿大</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">137</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁生日快乐！》《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">2003</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">年第二届加拿大国际儿童艺术展》（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">7</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">-9</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁组）银奖，作品被组委会收藏。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;" data-pm-slice="4 3 []"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">为了创作这幅作品，</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">7</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">岁的</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">Mona&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">在</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">2003</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">年</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">7</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">月</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">1</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">号这一天，在家长的陪同下，带着干粮到渥太华国会广场参加国庆节活动，从早上八点到晚上十点钟，观看了升旗仪式、游行、总理讲话、飞机空中表演、歌舞、街头艺术家的节目、晚上烟花秀。在画中的餐车买了热狗和柠檬水，下午瓢泼大雨，到附近的办公大楼避雨</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">，画了大量的速写。</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">Mona</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">体验生活，收集了丰富的素材，创作时胸有成竹，一挥而就。上百个人物出现在她的画面里。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;" data-pm-slice="4 3 []"><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7775229357798165" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-18.jpg" data-w="436" height="271" width="349"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">Mona Li (</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">李玥</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">) 8</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁 《我问外婆新年好！》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">2004</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">年多伦多国际儿童新春美术大赛》（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">7</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">-10</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁组）银奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8181818181818182" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-19.jpg" data-w="462" height="302" width="370"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0cm;margin-left: 36pt;text-align: center;line-height: 1em;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">Mona Li</span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf="">(</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">李玥</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">)</span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf="">11</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">《运功阳光，健身活力》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;line-height: 1em;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">2007</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">年第五届加拿大国际儿童艺术展》（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">11</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">-14</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁组）</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">金</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=""><span leaf=""><img alt="Screenshot_20251201_193441ab" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8431771894093686" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-20.jpg" data-w="491" height="331" width="393"></span></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: -26.85pt;margin-left: -37.6pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 宋体;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf="">Mona Li</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf="">（李玥）</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;12</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf="">岁 《我和福娃传圣火》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: -26.85pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">2008</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">年第六届加拿大国际儿童艺术展》（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">11-14</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁组）金 奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf=""><img alt="Screenshot_20251201_191434.ajpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8471910112359551" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-21.jpg" data-w="445" height="302" width="356"></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: -26.85pt;margin-left: -37.6pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 宋体;"><span style=""><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=""><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">Mona Li (</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">李</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">玥</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;)14</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">岁《</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;REBUILD</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">重建》</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span style=""><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">《</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">2010</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">年第八届加拿大国际儿童艺术节》</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;(11-14</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">岁组</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">)&nbsp;</span></span><span style=""><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">金</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">奖</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">Mona Li (&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">李玥</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">)&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">在</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">2010</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">年加拿大国际儿童艺术节上宣读她的获奖感言：</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);"><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">It’s a great honor to be receiving this award. I believe that the theme of this year’s exhibition was a great way to promote environmental issues to young people by simply getting us to think.</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);"><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span style="background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">The fetus at the centre of my drawing is there to make the point that the Earth is a very fragile thing, comparable to a fetus in the womb. Anything that happens on the outside of the Earth has a direct result on the health and wellbeing of the environment, as the fetus is vulnerable to all the actions of its mother. We, the inhabitants of the Earth, are responsible as caregivers to take care of the planet. We all know that mothers should not drink or smoke during pregnancy, and neither should humans be dumping pollutants into he air, water and soil. Whether or not we choose to face these issues is our own decision, but if we don’t work towards a more sustainable environment, life will generally be threatened, and frankly, everything may die.</span></span></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span style="background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">I could tell everybody to recycle, compost and turn off the lights, and these are all good things that you should do, but what may be the most effective would be to put pressure on large corporations in the industries that are jeopardizing our resources. The largest factors that affect the health of the environment are at economic and political levels and really involve the use of money. Saving the environment requires a long-term solution, not something that can be achieved over one or two years. As is portrayed by the toddlers in my drawing, restoring the Earth to its sustainable self will be responsible to our generation of youth and those to come.</span></span></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span style="background: white;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 17px;">I’d like to thank my parents – my mom, Lu Feng, for the guidance and support. I would also like to thank Lisa, my sister, for getting me to the ceremony. Finally, I’d like to thank the organizers for getting the exhibition going and for everyone else who came out to support the event.</span></span></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span style="background: white;"><span leaf="">Mona Li&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);background: white;"><span leaf="">（李玥）</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style="background: white;"><span leaf="">Aug 8,2010</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8362989323843416" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-22.jpg" data-w="562" height="376" width="450"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Aurelia Fulsom 6</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Birds on Planes, Trains in Hills</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">飞机上的鸟，山里的火车</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">2022</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">年第二十届加拿大国际儿童艺术节</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">》</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">6</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf="">岁以下组） 银 奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.824847250509165" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-23.jpg" data-w="491" height="324" style="width:451px;height:372px;" width="393"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Annie Li 9&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Love at the Bus Station&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">爱在汽车站》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" styl