-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁）铜</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8073593073593074" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-29.jpg" data-w="462" height="298" style="width:435px;height:351px;" width="370"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Corrine Yang 15</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Without Us</span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">没有我们》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">2022</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">第二十届加拿大国际儿童艺术节》（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">14</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">-17</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁组）金</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, ser