-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-32.jpg" data-w="400" height="320" style="width:393px;height:393px;" width="320"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Yiran Shen&nbsp;</span><span style=""></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">沈怡然</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;12</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">Timeless Dreams&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">永恒的梦想》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">AIGC&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">绘画</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">《</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">2024</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">第二十二届加拿大国际儿童艺术展》（</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">10</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf="">-13</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">岁组）银</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 宋体;"><span leaf="">奖</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8004073319755601" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-33.jpg" data-w="491" height="314" width="393"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">Reina Zhao&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">赵爰晰</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">13</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">岁 《</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">A Galaxy of Memories&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">记忆银河》水彩画</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">2024</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">第二十二届加拿大国际儿童艺术节》（</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">10</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">岁</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">-13</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">岁）铜 奖</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.1926345609065157" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-34.jpg" data-w="353" height="337" style="width:391px;height:466px;" width="282"></span></span></p><section><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">2003年至2025年，路风美术的同学们连续22年参加《加拿大国际儿童艺术展》等国际绘画比赛，近300人次。获金奖22个，银奖34个，铜奖53个，优秀奖89个，最佳创意奖15个，新人新作奖9个，最小年龄奖2个，最受欢迎奖2个，爱心大使奖1个，最美童心奖4个，最具潜力奖3个。路风老师连续22年荣获优秀指导老师奖，于2016年8月被加拿大国际儿童艺术展颁发伯乐终身成就奖。 路风美术于2012年11月接受渥太华电台专题采访，2022年接受加拿大WOW电视台专访。</span></p><o:p></o:p></b></section><p style="margin-right: -26.85pt;margin-left: -37.6pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""></span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7874015748031497" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-35.jpg" data-w="381" height="240" style="width:407px;height:320px;" width="305"></span><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-right: -26.85pt;margin-left: -37.6pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.782608695652174" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-36.jpg" data-w="276" height="173" style="width:409px;height:320px;" width="221"></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-right: -26.85pt;margin-left: -37.6pt;text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style=""><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.1065573770491803" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-37.jpg" data-w="488" height="432" style="width:424px;height:469px;" width="390"></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:
&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.5449871465295629" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-38.jpg" data-w="778" height="339" width="622"></span></span></p><section><span leaf=""><br  /></span></section><section><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">主持人：为何您的教育宗旨不是“培养艺术家”，而是“培养具备观察力与创意力的人”？</span></p><span leaf=""><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">路风：在当今全球化的竞争，比赛的是大脑---创意。创意人，是企业的救星，是商场的强人 。个人认为，创意教育不专属于培养艺术家而存在，它可以是培养有高感性能力、创造能力、同理心、右脑活跃适应社会各界有开拓素质的人才的。我们每年参加《加拿大国际儿童艺术节绘画比赛》，就是初来乍到路风美术的同学，都可以参加比赛，并且取得好成绩。参加创作比赛在先，绘画基本功教学后来进行。因为，青少年儿童的想象力是与生俱来的，就看老师和家长如去何引导和保护。那么，通过学习绘画基本功，训练和提高我们的观察能力、分析能力、理解能力、表现能力，来提高我们的审美，能够更好地诠释想象力。通过艺术创作活跃我们天马行空的想象力和学习能力。时至今日，“创意在先，基本功教学后来” 的美术教育行之有效。不敢说日后诺贝尔奖的皇冠会戴在同学们的头上，起码腾校、名校青睐有创造能力、有艺术气质、关爱社会公益的青少年是不争的事实。</span></p><span leaf=""><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">所以，我们不只是培养艺术家，而是培养具有强有力的观察能力有创意头脑的各科人才。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8185595567867036" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-39.jpg" data-w="722" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《油画写生帆船俱乐部》作者：高璐，九年级学生，2003.8</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7452229299363057" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-40.jpg" data-w="785" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《油画建筑写生》作者：高璐，2003.8.</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.750332005312085" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-41.jpg" data-w="753" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《水彩风景写生港湾》作者：吴真真，2003.8.</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7545454545454545" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-42.jpg" data-w="550" style="width:578px;height:436px;" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《水彩风景写生帆船俱乐部》作者：许砾丹 小学生 2003.8.</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.78625" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-43.jpg" data-w="800" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《线描建筑写生》作者：Mona Li 7岁，2003.8</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8200782268578879" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-44.jpg" data-w="767" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《油画户外建筑写生》作者：赵露 小学生2003年8月</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-45.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.2698412698412698" data-w="441" type="block"  /></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《水彩画户外船舶写生》作者：陶嘉纪，小学生2003年8月</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.775" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-46.jpg" data-w="800" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《水彩画户外写生》作者：陶嘉念，2003年8月</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7727717923604309" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-47.jpg" data-w="1021" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《户外线描写生建筑》作者：李享，2003年8月</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.6925" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-48.jpg" data-w="800" type="block"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《户外风景线描写生》作者：洋洋，2003年8月</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.79375" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-49.jpg" data-w="800" type="block"></section><section><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf="" data-pm-slice="1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;b&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《户外风景线描写生》作者：崔婧，2003年7月</span></span></p></b></section><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">主持人：今年您将带学生参加渥太华第三届生肖绘画比赛，这次准备有什么特别之处？</span></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;"><br  /></span></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">从文化上，从历史上，从故事中去了解生肖。打开创作思路，学生立刻就会联系实际说出家人与生肖的有关情感，有关联系，形象思维在脑子里形成画面。鼓励学生积极参与创作，在客观条件允许的情况下，做一个有激情去表达自己观点的社会主人翁。每一次参加画展，都是一次文化课学习，包括历史、地理、人文风俗。路风美术在参加《2025第二届渥太华生肖绘画比赛（蛇年）》时，主动参与，积极创作，除了外地网课的学生，线下有24位同学递交了制作精美，创意新颖的作品参加比赛。同时体会了与社区的文化交流与互动，家长和同学做义工布置会场、做节目主持人，做力所能及的社区服务工作。路风老师在颁奖会场搞个人画展，宣传少数民族的艺术与绘画的表现形式。</span></b></p><section><span leaf=""><br  /></span></section><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="line-height: 1.38;font-weight: normal;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8105906313645621" src="spotlight-lufeng/lufeng-50.jpg" data-w="491" height="318" style="width:447px;height:362px;" width="393"></span></span><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">Avery Kwan 9</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">岁 《金蛇献瑞》&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">《</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">2025</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">第二届渥太华青少年生肖绘画比赛（蛇年）》</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;B&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">组 金奖</span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sa